column1: Courtesy of YouTube

Game of Thrones may be more known for its shocking twists, horrific deaths and nudity. But fans of the fantasy series are just as enthralled by the simple conversations that the characters have with each other. Watching them trade barbs and insults, as well as veiled threats, can be as exciting as dragons laying waste to an entire city.

Lena Headey and Jimmy Kimmel Have GAME OF THRONES Style Battle of Wine and Insults #GoT
Cersei Lannister is the queen of mean and she’s not afraid to throw down!

When actress Lena Headey visited Jimmy Kimmel Live, the host challenged her to a round of wine in goblets and a battle of GAME OF THRONES style insults. Knowing her prowess with the two, Jimmy was sure to lose, but the moment was absolutely hilarious!
